[Ethlizards Genesis Collection](https://opensea.io/collection/genesis-ethlizards-erc721) | [Ethlizards Honorary Collection](https://opensea.io/collection/honoraryethlizards) | [Website](https://www.ethlizards.io/) | [Discord](https://discord.com/invite/ethlizards) | [Twitter](https://twitter.com/ethlizards)

The Ethlizards is a collectors club with immense utility to back their status as pioneers in the emerging field of GameFi.

An Ethlizards grants the collector entry to our exclusive Underground Lounge and community where likeminded contributors discuss everything GameFi, collectables and Web3.

Come hang out, enjoy the atmosphere and make your friends jealous. The lounge is always open to its venerated members.

CryptoMories
collection.description:
"memento mori" means " remember you die" in latin. 
It is an old saying used to remind people that life is short, and must be lived to the fullest.
It is very often symbolized by a skull.
CryptoMories are 10 000 little skeletons here to remind you that life is good, that there are a lot of amazingly kind people, and that you are one of them. Focus on your greatness.

CryptoMories are not a basic 10k generative series. They are an adaptative generative series. 
One item differs from one Mori to another, depending on the type. A top hat on a zombie will have holes in it. This makes different types even more special. And it is extremely fun to try to figure out what item looks like on other types.

Also, there are many little fun games and easter eggs. Including VERY special Mories.. some might say unique..

CryptoMories are the second series of the iwwon project, after the Los Samos handmade one. Both can be combine to access the handmade series vandals. See more on discord.

Voxies
collection.description:
Voxies are cute, lovable and collectible 3d voxel buddies, that live and play on the Ethereum blockchain. There are only 10,000 Voxies in existence and no two Voxies are identical. Lots of random properties and fun traits make each Voxie cute, unique and sometimes rare!

Voxies are not just a collectible but are also the first and only NFT to be fully integrated with a playable RPG turn-based tactical game. Bring your owned Voxies to life in Voxie Tactics as you collect, battle, and earn rewards in the Voxiverse. VOXEL tokens are used as the currency in Voxie Tactics and used to buy/trade on the Voxies marketplace.

Lil' Heroes by Edgar Plans
collection.description:
Edgar Plans is coming to the metaverse! The Spanish contemporary artist has been designing a collection of 7,777 pieces to reflect his work of the past decade. Meet Lil Heroes, the mouse-eared mischievous characters dressed in a huge variety of unique hand-drawn attributes.

Edgar Plans (born 1977 in Madrid) is a spanish contemporary visual artist. Painter from a very young age, he delivers pure artistic expression in childlike art pieces. His vivid and raw cartoons glean elements from the works of american icons Jean-Michel Basquiat and Keith Haring. Currently displayed in the Moscow Museum of Modern Art, his artworks are sought after around the world, ending up breaking records in auction houses like Christies.
